      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MYSTIC PIXEL (8) drew a squeeze box and was game in defeat when a close third, one length from the winner Sensational Star (17.41) at this track. Sure to be about the mark. ITA KEEPING (6) showed blistering pace early and gave a sight when in the minors, beaten 0.8 lengths over 300m this track in 17.38. Can feature again. ZETA PRIME (3) had to overcome a collision with another runner and could manage only a distant eighth (24.11) in a Grade 6 over 400m at this track. Should be in this for a long way. GLOW GIRL (1) should bounce back after an unplaced effort here recently.",
